name: 路易斯·希利

last_movies.title: 小羽毛海蒂 第一季

introduction: AboutYoungest son of soap opera actress Denise Welch and television actor Tim Healy. He is also the brother of singer Matthew Healy of The 1975. He is an actor with credits that include the TV series Hetty Feather and Doctors.Before FameHe was born Louis Vincent Healy in Salford, England.TriviaFollowing in the footsteps of his brother, some of his musical performances have been published to YouTube.Family LifeHis parents separated in 2012, and his mother began dating Lincoln Townley shortly after. His mother and Townley would marry in July of 2013.Associated WithHis brother Matthew Healy fronts the popular English band The 1975.
